For the past few weeks, I have been trying out a couple of products from @listenskincare - Formulated specially for Indian Skin . 
Lisén is also: 
-Not Tested on Animals
-Paraben Free

I am actually really happy with the results and my skin shows through the glow it reflects ✨

1. #BluePowerhouse - Hyaluronic Acid Ampoule targeting my dry skin.

2. #RevealingGrace - Eye cream targeting my undereye area

3. #PureGenius - Peel Stick targeting my blackheads and whiteheads

Do you want even-toned skin for your next vacay pictures just like Alia Bhatt? Here’s what I do to keep sun-tan at bay and have even toned arms for my next vacation ! 
Only 3 steps : 

1. Sunscreen: apply and reapply your sunscreen, every two hours and sunscreen should not just be for your face, but your body as well every time you step outdoors. 

2. Keep your skin away from products that rip your skin off moisture and disrupt your pH balance. Instead try keeping your skin hydrated which protects your skin barrier . 

3. Keep a body wash  handy that tackles  tanning without being harsh on your skin . I recently discovered  @myplixlife pineapple smoothie skin body wash and this has helped in ways I cant describe. It smells beautiful by the way and exfoliates my skin gently without drying it out & removing tan . I have loved making this a part of my shower routine & already purchased the next bottle !!
